     Author: Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)
     Contributors: Claude (Anthropic)
     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Synthwave '84 theme. Retro-futuristic
         80s VHS aesthetic: deep purple (#262335) background with neon pink (#FF7EDB),
         cyan (#03EDF9), orange (#FF8B39) and green (#72F1B8) accents.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in Synthwave84Theme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

